products.title: Azurite Chenille Grey Curtain
products.description: Their azurite chenille range consists of textured plains with a velour soft-feel finish. This soft grey fabric fuses a plush, luxury feel in a contemporary grey tone to create a on trend room feature that is bound to be noticed. These curtains will look beautiful in cool, contemporary spaces & are perfect for adding shade and texturing to grey styled interiors. All their curtains are lovingly handmade within the uk.
